    <node id="source3.Project_Registry">
      <data key="d0">source3.Project_Registry</data>
      <data key="d1">TABLE</data>
      <data key="d2">The Project_Registry.csv table contains information about various projects, including the fiscal year they were registered in, the programming process, project status, organization details such as class and type, sector and continent names, project spending amounts, and various markers indicating the presence or absence of specific themes or types of aid. Each project is associated with a unique project number, section, and branch ID, along with detailed division and fund center information.</data>
